---
title: Beef Ragù Penne with Zucchini, Parmesan, and Pepperolio
description: Penne with tomato sauce is always a recipe for success. Is there anyone who’d turn down a plate of pasta piled high and dusted with cheese? Surely not, although adding some extra meat and veg certainly makes it all the more crave-able. Which is exactly what we’re doing: taking a tried-and-true Italian American classic and giving it hearty ground beef and bites of tender zucchini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-ragu-spaghetti-9b21e3e3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/beef-ragu-spaghetti-5ade613230006c2f340c3822-82f5e7c7.pdf
